WATCH: Philippine Air Force now has 6 fighter jets Two brand new FA-50 jets of the Philippine Air Force arrive on Wednesday, February 22 Published 3:44 PM, February 22, 2017 Updated 3:44 PM, February 22, 2017 
Two more brand new FA-50 lead-in fighter trainers of the Philippine Air Force arrived at the Clark Air Base in Pampanga on Wednesday, February 22.
